    "name": "银河摸鱼人 ",
    "steam_appid": 1731000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/95a8fcc0753010492d55cd4573b345ef.avif?t=1766642675\" width=564 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏介绍：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《银河摸鱼人》是一款融合了钓鱼探索和道具收集元素的休闲钓鱼游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为玩家的你，将扮演一个不想工作只想钓鱼的星际猎人“斯高克”，在异星享受舒适的摸鱼时间，相遇形形色色的外星文明角色，了解他们的喜好与故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，玩家可以搭配丰富的钓鱼装备，组合出不同流派的装备搭配效果，以便于决策出当前需要的探索属性。最终顺利收集星球上的丰富钓物，并完成不同角色向你发出的委托请求。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2687 </strong>种丰富的收集元素，满足玩家纯粹的收集欲望，并让时间不知不觉中快速流逝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/de9cca7c4491d87d49a4c4cea5974466.poster.avif?t=1766642675\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/de9cca7c4491d87d49a4c4cea5974466.webm?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/de9cca7c4491d87d49a4c4cea5974466.mp4?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >骰子掷点形式的探索体验，通过点数决策钓点，触发各式各样的特殊事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/a40ff829d6431ef6455d9cbdd75e849f.poster.avif?t=1766642675\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/a40ff829d6431ef6455d9cbdd75e849f.webm?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/a40ff829d6431ef6455d9cbdd75e849f.mp4?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种操作各异的钓鱼技法，每一次调整截然不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/6c2b8c00c1197df776735b9f5bdcf25c.poster.avif?t=1766642675\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/6c2b8c00c1197df776735b9f5bdcf25c.webm?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/6c2b8c00c1197df776735b9f5bdcf25c.mp4?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >布置专属于你的桌面鱼缸，尺寸大小、位置摆放、鱼类选择，造景布置，皆由你自行决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/5cee1c9f4e9144d1a74c5c39ead79625.poster.avif?t=1766642675\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/5cee1c9f4e9144d1a74c5c39ead79625.webm?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/5cee1c9f4e9144d1a74c5c39ead79625.mp4?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有迷你游戏与各种趣味的应用程序，打发多余的时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/fa2f0182d5e9317c8ff7f654892253c7.poster.avif?t=1766642675\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/fa2f0182d5e9317c8ff7f654892253c7.webm?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/fa2f0182d5e9317c8ff7f654892253c7.mp4?t=1766642675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>最后：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您正在寻找一款消磨时间的上班摸鱼游戏，《银河摸鱼人》将成为你最佳的选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你热衷在各类游戏中无休止的钓鱼，《银河摸鱼人》将直接满足你的需求。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你收集成瘾，《银河摸鱼人》也会让你停不下来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你已经看到了这里，可以先将《银河摸鱼人》添加至你的愿望单了。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是对我们最大的支持和认同，谢谢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731000/extras/2fae04d03666de676a63bd1415d4e2ef.avif?t=1766642675\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li></ul>",
